WEBVTT

00:00:00.240 --> 00:00:04.070
I saw that there's something coming, and

00:00:04.080 --> 00:00:08.230
it's revolving around the three

00:00:08.230 --> 00:00:08.240
I-Atlas.

00:00:08.240 --> 00:00:11.350
It's connected.

00:00:11.360 --> 00:00:14.870
Whatever this is is connected.

00:00:14.880 --> 00:00:17.349
And the Lord said we're about to see

00:00:17.359 --> 00:00:18.950
something

00:00:18.950 --> 00:00:18.960
that's

00:00:18.960 --> 00:00:21.590
going to freak people out.

00:00:21.600 --> 00:00:25.509
I saw the fire. I saw

00:00:27.199 --> 00:00:30.150
what he said was a shaking; it's going to be a

00:00:30.160 --> 00:00:32.870
call to wake up everybody. And what we're

00:00:32.880 --> 00:00:34.950
about to see in the heavens is a shaking

00:00:34.960 --> 00:00:37.590
in the heavens. He said it's going

00:00:37.600 --> 00:00:39.510
to be like blood; it's about fire and

00:00:39.520 --> 00:00:41.750
it's so loud.

00:00:41.760 --> 00:00:44.389
This is a major event

00:00:44.399 --> 00:00:46.549
that's about to take place. Something is

00:00:46.559 --> 00:00:50.549
coming, soon it's

00:00:50.549 --> 00:00:50.559
coming, and

00:00:50.559 --> 00:00:53.590
this is not

00:00:53.600 --> 00:00:55.270
an alien.

00:00:55.280 --> 00:00:57.910
There's no such thing as aliens; it's

00:00:57.920 --> 00:01:00.709
demonic spirits.

00:01:00.719 --> 00:01:03.110
But what you're about to see is what

00:01:03.120 --> 00:01:05.990
Oral Roberts saw

00:01:06.000 --> 00:01:09.910
in 2004, called the 'Wake-up

00:01:09.910 --> 00:01:09.920
Call.'It

00:01:09.920 --> 00:01:12.710
will be a wake-up to the

00:01:12.720 --> 00:01:14.550
church,

00:01:14.560 --> 00:01:18.149
a wake-up to the world,

00:01:18.159 --> 00:01:20.550
a sign of the second coming of the Lord

00:01:20.560 --> 00:01:24.710
Jesus Christ. It's time for preachers

00:01:24.720 --> 00:01:27.749
to preach fire back in the pulpits,

00:01:27.759 --> 00:01:29.749
to preach repentance back in the

00:01:29.759 --> 00:01:32.390
pulpits.

00:01:32.400 --> 00:01:36.390
For there will be a sign in the heavens.

00:01:36.400 --> 00:01:38.230
There will be a sign throughout the

00:01:38.240 --> 00:01:41.429
earth. Remember this

00:01:41.439 --> 00:01:46.149
word.

00:01:46.159 --> 00:01:49.030
Timing was not right. You know, whenever

00:01:49.040 --> 00:01:51.510
you're seeing over in the spirit, it looks

00:01:51.520 --> 00:01:53.590
like it's right in front of your face,

00:01:53.600 --> 00:01:56.310
but there's something coming. And most

00:01:56.320 --> 00:01:59.190
of them know that it's

00:01:59.190 --> 00:01:59.200
coming—government—and

00:01:59.200 --> 00:02:02.230
it's not

00:02:02.240 --> 00:02:03.990
conspiracy. No, it's

00:02:04.000 --> 00:02:05.830
not conspiracy. That's what the Spirit

00:02:05.840 --> 00:02:07.429
of the Lord just said. He said this is

00:02:07.439 --> 00:02:09.749
not conspiracy;

00:02:09.759 --> 00:02:11.510
it's a sign of the second coming of the

00:02:11.520 --> 00:02:13.910
Lord Jesus Christ. It's awakening up the

00:02:13.920 --> 00:02:17.589
world. Then I saw with my eyes something

00:02:17.599 --> 00:02:20.550
I'd never seen:

00:02:20.560 --> 00:02:22.229
suddenly

00:02:22.239 --> 00:02:25.430
in the clouds, in the skies

00:02:25.440 --> 00:02:29.190
above New York City and the east part of

00:02:29.200 --> 00:02:31.350
the United States,

00:02:31.360 --> 00:02:35.589
which hung there for quite some time

00:02:35.599 --> 00:02:38.949
and then spread out across America

00:02:38.959 --> 00:02:41.670
without touching the ground.

00:02:41.680 --> 00:02:45.270
Then God diffused it away from

00:02:45.280 --> 00:02:48.309
America and sent it out to the nations

00:02:48.319 --> 00:02:50.869
of the earth.

00:02:50.879 --> 00:02:53.350
And I saw

00:02:53.360 --> 00:02:55.350
and I heard.

00:02:58.000 --> 00:03:01.990
I saw something coming down from above:

00:03:02.000 --> 00:03:05.270
smoke and vapor

00:03:05.280 --> 00:03:09.190
and blood. Or it looked like that

00:03:09.200 --> 00:03:12.710
to my spiritual eyes.

00:03:12.720 --> 00:03:17.910
There it was hanging so huge until it

00:03:17.920 --> 00:03:22.149
almost blotted out the sky.

00:03:22.159 --> 00:03:25.350
Instantly I thought about

00:03:25.360 --> 00:03:27.430
9/11

00:03:27.440 --> 00:03:29.430
when the terrorists attacked the Twin

00:03:29.440 --> 00:03:33.670
Towers. First, I saw this thing

00:03:33.680 --> 00:03:35.350
hovering

00:03:35.360 --> 00:03:38.470
and great changes coming in it to where

00:03:38.480 --> 00:03:42.710
I couldn't miss it. And then I heard

00:03:42.720 --> 00:03:46.869
something come into my ears, and it

00:03:46.879 --> 00:03:49.350
reminded me of what a friend of mine had

00:03:49.360 --> 00:03:53.990
said when the first space

00:03:54.000 --> 00:03:55.589
capsule

00:03:55.599 --> 00:03:59.190
was released into the sky.

00:03:59.200 --> 00:04:02.390
They told me that they made all of

00:04:02.390 --> 00:04:02.400
them—he

00:04:02.400 --> 00:04:05.910
was a newsman in New York

00:04:05.910 --> 00:04:05.920
City—be

00:04:05.920 --> 00:04:10.789
maybe half a mile or more away

00:04:10.799 --> 00:04:13.830
from the capsule.

00:04:13.840 --> 00:04:16.150
And he said when that thing lifted off

00:04:16.160 --> 00:04:20.789
the earth, there was a sound, and the

00:04:20.799 --> 00:04:25.270
sound itself moved the weeds and the

00:04:25.280 --> 00:04:29.430
growth. And he said, 'It penetrated

00:04:29.440 --> 00:04:32.790
my body.'He said as I talked to others,

00:04:32.800 --> 00:04:35.189
they felt the same thing. He said the

00:04:35.199 --> 00:04:39.749
sound was so enormous that nothing had

00:04:39.759 --> 00:04:42.070
ever happened like it in the history of

00:04:42.080 --> 00:04:44.870
the world. Instantly, I thought of that

00:04:44.880 --> 00:04:46.710
because the sound that was coming

00:04:46.720 --> 00:04:50.469
into my ears was penetrating my whole

00:04:50.479 --> 00:04:52.870
being.

00:04:52.880 --> 00:04:56.469
And then I heard God's voice.

00:04:56.479 --> 00:05:01.350
He said, 'I'm making a

00:05:01.350 --> 00:05:01.360
sign.'This

00:05:01.360 --> 00:05:03.670
is a sign according to the second

00:05:03.680 --> 00:05:06.950
chapter of Acts where the Apostle Peter,

00:05:06.960 --> 00:05:09.909
upon the giving of

00:05:09.919 --> 00:05:11.909
the Holy Spirit, the baptism of the Holy

00:05:11.919 --> 00:05:12.870
Spirit,

00:05:12.880 --> 00:05:14.870
said there'll be signs

00:05:15.360 --> 00:05:16.469
in the skies.

00:05:16.479 --> 00:05:18.790
He said, 'This is one of the

00:05:18.800 --> 00:05:23.590
signs of the end time because

00:05:23.600 --> 00:05:26.950
the world is not ready for the second

00:05:26.960 --> 00:05:29.670
coming of my Son.'They are coming to

00:05:29.680 --> 00:05:32.870
church on Sunday morning mostly for

00:05:32.880 --> 00:05:34.550
themselves.

00:05:34.560 --> 00:05:37.990
And the preachers, for the most part, are

00:05:38.000 --> 00:05:40.390
not really concerned about the nations

00:05:40.400 --> 00:05:43.189
of the earth; they're concerned about

00:05:43.199 --> 00:05:46.390
the little group that is there. They

00:05:46.400 --> 00:05:48.390
sing their songs and they get up

00:05:48.400 --> 00:05:53.510
and preach. When 9/11 struck,

00:05:53.520 --> 00:05:56.390
there was a fear that came

00:05:56.400 --> 00:05:59.510
into their hearts—even of my people

00:05:59.520 --> 00:06:02.950
of the church and of people outside the

00:06:02.950 --> 00:06:02.960
church—and

00:06:02.960 --> 00:06:07.029
millions the following Sunday

00:06:07.039 --> 00:06:09.909
rushed to go to church.

00:06:09.919 --> 00:06:12.390
That's right. But the preachers were not

00:06:12.400 --> 00:06:15.430
prepared, and most of them didn't even

00:06:15.440 --> 00:06:17.830
preach on it and didn't even talk about

00:06:17.840 --> 00:06:21.350
it being the sign of something that's

00:06:21.360 --> 00:06:23.990
coming

00:06:24.000 --> 00:06:27.990
hundreds of thousands of times bigger.

00:06:28.000 --> 00:06:31.510
He said when those planes of the

00:06:31.520 --> 00:06:34.790
terrorists struck the Twin Towers in New

00:06:34.800 --> 00:06:38.070
York City and they gradually came

00:06:38.080 --> 00:06:40.550
tumbling down,

00:06:40.560 --> 00:06:42.870
it was something bigger than people had

00:06:42.880 --> 00:06:45.350
ever seen. But it's

00:06:45.360 --> 00:06:48.870
nothing in comparison to what's going to

00:06:48.880 --> 00:06:53.590
happen in the second coming of my Son.

00:06:53.600 --> 00:06:56.950
And so he said, 'My church was not

00:06:56.960 --> 00:06:59.670
prepared to deal with that.'And people

00:06:59.680 --> 00:07:02.230
came to church and then nothing much

00:07:02.240 --> 00:07:04.230
happened, and they dropped back and many

00:07:04.240 --> 00:07:05.749
of them went back to their

00:07:05.749 --> 00:07:05.759
beds.

00:07:05.759 --> 00:07:08.710
There's a sign coming, a sign for the

00:07:08.720 --> 00:07:12.309
unbeliever. A sign for the unbeliever is

00:07:12.319 --> 00:07:14.870
coming. A sign.

00:07:14.880 --> 00:07:17.029
It's time to get on the boat. I've

00:07:17.039 --> 00:07:19.670
warned and warned and warned that within

00:07:19.680 --> 00:07:22.070
a 24-hour period, everything would

00:07:22.080 --> 00:07:25.830
change. Everything is going to change

00:07:25.840 --> 00:07:28.710
within a 24-hour period. The way you

00:07:28.720 --> 00:07:30.629
live life, everything is going to

00:07:30.639 --> 00:07:33.350
change. Where there'll be signs in the

00:07:33.360 --> 00:07:37.110
heavens, there'll be signs in the earth.

00:07:37.120 --> 00:07:39.749
There'll be signs in your politics,

00:07:39.759 --> 00:07:42.309
there'll be signs in your finances, and

00:07:42.319 --> 00:07:44.469
there'll be signs in your church.

00:07:44.479 --> 00:07:47.350
Sorrows. This is the

00:07:47.360 --> 00:07:49.830
beginning of sorrows—the labor

00:07:49.840 --> 00:07:53.350
pains upon a woman. So will it be. He's

00:07:53.360 --> 00:07:55.589
doing it out of mercy.

00:07:55.599 --> 00:07:59.029
He will do this out of love,

00:07:59.039 --> 00:08:01.990
and the

00:08:02.000 --> 00:08:04.629
church bells will ring. You'll see

00:08:04.629 --> 00:08:04.639
people—remember

00:08:04.639 --> 00:08:07.670
9/11, how they all

00:08:07.680 --> 00:08:10.390
ran to church?

00:08:10.400 --> 00:08:12.469
It was the way, when Charlie Kirk

00:08:12.469 --> 00:08:12.479
died,

00:08:12.479 --> 00:08:14.869
they ran to church. But when you see

00:08:14.879 --> 00:08:18.710
these signs, they will run. But what

00:08:18.720 --> 00:08:21.110
will they get? When these signs

00:08:21.120 --> 00:08:23.670
come,

00:08:23.680 --> 00:08:26.390
you must stay filled.

00:08:26.400 --> 00:08:29.749
You must stay filled for they're coming

00:08:29.759 --> 00:08:33.829
in hot. You must stay filled, my

00:08:33.839 --> 00:08:37.509
harvesters.

00:08:37.519 --> 00:08:39.909
For the harvest is plentiful and the

00:08:39.909 --> 00:08:39.919
laborers

00:08:39.919 --> 00:08:43.430
