00:09:09.839 --> 00:09:13.190
this is his mercy and

00:09:13.200 --> 00:09:17.750
his grace. One last push, one last call.

00:09:17.760 --> 00:09:21.030
It's going to

00:09:21.040 --> 00:09:24.150
shake the world. He's going to

00:09:24.160 --> 00:09:26.949
make a sign.

00:09:26.959 --> 00:09:30.230
It's so loud in me.

00:09:30.240 --> 00:09:33.590
I hear it so loud. There's a major

00:09:33.600 --> 00:09:37.430
event

00:09:37.440 --> 00:09:42.070
about to take place.

00:09:42.080 --> 00:09:44.949
Fearful sights you will see that will

