bring you to your knee.

00:09:51.440 --> 00:09:55.269
It's going to be a sign

00:09:55.269 --> 00:09:55.279
that

00:09:55.279 --> 00:09:57.910
the coming of the

00:09:57.920 --> 00:10:00.790
Lord Jesus Christ is at hand. The devils

