00:10:03.670 --> 00:10:03.680
is

00:10:03.680 --> 00:10:05.350
the theme tonight. You need

00:10:05.360 --> 00:10:07.110
to understand what the Lord is trying to

00:10:07.120 --> 00:10:10.790
tell you.

00:10:10.800 --> 00:10:11.750
Revelation

00:10:11.760 --> 00:10:14.470
12...

00:10:14.480 --> 00:10:17.110
read it one more time, love.

00:10:17.120 --> 00:10:20.150
Revelation

00:10:20.160 --> 00:10:24.310
12:12. Satan knows.

00:10:24.320 --> 00:10:26.630
He knows.

