00:13:51.829 --> 00:13:51.839
pray."I

00:13:51.839 --> 00:13:56.150
saw Oklahoma even being divided.

00:13:56.160 --> 00:13:58.150
I saw Texas with borders all around

00:13:58.160 --> 00:14:01.509
them, not wanting to secede from

00:14:01.519 --> 00:14:03.350
the United States, wanting to

00:14:03.360 --> 00:14:05.189
have their own country like we're

00:14:05.199 --> 00:14:06.710
not going to go this way.

00:14:06.720 --> 00:14:09.110
Secede.

00:14:09.120 --> 00:14:12.710
I saw people very upset with Gavin,

00:14:12.720 --> 00:14:16.069
and I saw a red wave trying to

00:14:16.079 --> 00:14:18.069
come over California with people upset,

00:14:18.079 --> 00:14:19.829
saying, "Listen, we're taking back our

00:14:19.839 --> 00:14:22.949
state."So,

00:14:22.959 --> 00:14:26.310
we must pray ahead of time. I

00:14:26.320 --> 00:14:27.910
know we have a year and we'll pray into it

00:14:27.920 --> 00:14:30.389
a lot over the next year, but I

00:14:30.399 --> 00:14:33.269
have such an urgency to tell you we must

00:14:33.279 --> 00:14:34.870
keep

00:14:34.880 --> 00:14:37.670
even more of a majority in the Senate

00:14:37.680 --> 00:14:40.150
and in the House to pass forth

00:14:40.160 --> 00:14:43.189
legislation to get the job done that

00:14:43.199 --> 00:14:45.910
needs to be done so that we have all the

00:14:45.920 --> 00:14:49.199
things that we need."

